{
  "texts": [
    "Since Chat-GPT is an emerging technology, administrators at the university where the research was conducted were concerned about its implementation in classes.",
    "Consequently, they allowed researchers to use it only in a single classroom.",
    "Therefore, the research was conducted with volunteers from one researcher's class.",
    "The reason for the online class was the state of emergency distance education after a massive earthquake hit Turkey on 6 February 2023.",
    "The demographic characteristics of the participants are presented in Table 1."
  ]
}